ined</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖則係鬼佬玩先但的確好多韓國明星/仔都有玩<br />\n而香港人接觸泡菜嘢較多先會咁睇<br />\n樓主貼嗰個都係泡茶仔冇睇錯嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白既 所以而家都廢事解釋咁多<br />\n識野既自然會明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d149cedef3a7da766005dbb03ec039af91c4772","tid":32182,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實呢<br />\n樣真係決定哂所有野<br />\n其次係身材<br />\n<br />\n樣衰或者肥就真係唔好攪咁多<br />\n<br />\n你係樣衰既，全身名牌都係柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你仲入黎潮流台做咩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通無錢就唔入得車行睇車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只不過係有時係街見到有班人著到奇奇呢呢，登台咩家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSpin去邊？關咩冇錢事 你係講緊冇錢買衫咩？<br />\n你個logic係覺得識著衫係冇用<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你用車行做例子 <br />\n係講緊車係垃圾 行路最好 但又入車行睇車"},{"pid":"cd5929dfe7b5b6e07918db5edb383dc119765adc","tid":32182,"uid":66201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你仲入黎潮流台做咩呀</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通無錢就唔入得車行睇車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只不過係有時係街見到有班人著到奇奇呢呢，登台咩家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSpin去邊？關咩冇錢事 你係講緊冇錢買衫咩？<br />\n你個logic係覺得識著衫係冇用<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你用車行做例子 <br />\n係講緊車係垃圾 行路最好 但又入車行睇車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我原意係回應緊你依句<br />\n<br />\n麻煩貼下樣衰/肥既香港人係著得好睇既黎睇下"},{"pid":"6ffe76f367caa27a2190c39f8e4a9a021a33164d","tid":32182,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"咁貴點買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /